This is a simple web-based calculator built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
It supports basic arithmetic operations as well as advanced functions like square root, power, logarithm (log base 10), and natural log (ln).
It also includes a light/dark mode toggle for better usability.

✨ Features

➕➖✖️➗ Basic arithmetic operations

√ Square root

^ Power function

log Logarithm (base 10)

ln Natural log

🌓 Light/Dark mode toggle

⌫ Backspace and Clear functions

🛠️ Technologies Used

HTML5 – Structure of the calculator

CSS3 – Styling, light & dark themes

JavaScript (ES6) – Calculator logic and theme toggle

🚀 How to Run

Download or copy the project files.

Open the index.html file in any modern web browser.

Start using the calculator!

